21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_in_srv(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 dns_name_t name;
25 isc_buffer_t buffer;
26 bool ok;
27
28 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
29 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
30
31 UNUSED(type);
32 UNUSED(rdclass);
33 UNUSED(callbacks);
34
35 /*
36 * Priority.
37 */
38 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
39 false));
40 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
41 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
42 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
43
44 /*
45 * Weight.
46 */
47 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
48 false));
49 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
50 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
51 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
52
53 /*
54 * Port.
55 */
56 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
57 false));
58 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
59 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
60 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
61
62 /*
63 * Target.
64 */
65 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
66 false));
67 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
68 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
69 if (origin == NULL)
70 origin = dns_rootname;
71 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
72 ok = true;
73 if ((options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMES) != 0)
74 ok = dns_name_ishostname(&name, false);
75 if (!ok && (options & DNS_RDATA_CHECKNAMESFAIL) != 0)
76 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADNAME);
77 if (!ok && callbacks != NULL)
78 warn_badname(&name, lexer, callbacks);
79 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
80}

82static inline isc_result_t
83totext_in_srv(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
84 isc_region_t region;
85 dns_name_t name;
86 dns_name_t prefix;
87 bool sub;
88 char buf[sizeof("64000")];
89 unsigned short num;
90
91 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
92 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
93 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
94
95 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
96 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
97
98 /*
99 * Priority.
100 */
101 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
102 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
103 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
104 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
105 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
106 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
107
108 /*
109 * Weight.
110 */
111 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
112 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
113 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
114 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
115 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
116
117 /*
118 * Port.
119 */
120 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
121 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
122 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
123 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
124 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
125
126 /*
127 * Target.
128 */
129 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
130 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
131 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
132}

134static inline isc_result_t
135fromwire_in_srv(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
136 dns_name_t name;
137 isc_region_t sr;
138
139 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
140 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
141
142 UNUSED(type);
143 UNUSED(rdclass);
144
145 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
146
147 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
148
149 /*
150 * Priority, weight, port.
151 */
152 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
153 if (sr.length < 6)
154 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
155 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 6));
156 isc_buffer_forward(source, 6);
157
158 /*
159 * Target.
160 */
161 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
162}
163
164static inline isc_result_t
165towire_in_srv(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
166 dns_name_t name;
167 dns_offsets_t offsets;
168 isc_region_t sr;
169
170 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
171 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
172
173 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
174 /*
175 * Priority, weight, port.
176 */
177 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
178 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 6));
179 isc_region_consume(&sr, 6);
180
181 /*
182 * Target.
183 */
184 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
185 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
186 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
187}

189static inline int
190compare_in_srv(ARGS_COMPARE) {
191 dns_name_t name1;
192 dns_name_t name2;
193 isc_region_t region1;
194 isc_region_t region2;
195 int order;
196
197 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
198 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
199 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
200 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
201 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
202 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
203
204 /*
205 * Priority, weight, port.
206 */
207 order = memcmp(rdata1->data, rdata2->data, 6);
208 if (order != 0)
209 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
210
211 /*
212 * Target.
213 */
214 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
215 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
216
217 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
218 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
219
220 isc_region_consume(&region1, 6);
221 isc_region_consume(&region2, 6);
222
223 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
224 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
225
226 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
227}
228
229static inline isc_result_t
230fromstruct_in_srv(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
231 dns_rdata_in_srv_t *srv = source;
232 isc_region_t region;
233
234 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
235 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
236 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
237 REQUIRE(srv->common.rdtype == type);
238 REQUIRE(srv->common.rdclass == rdclass);
239
240 UNUSED(type);
241 UNUSED(rdclass);
242
243 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(srv->priority, target));
244 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(srv->weight, target));
245 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(srv->port, target));
246 dns_name_toregion(&srv->target, &region);
247 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
248}
249
250static inline isc_result_t
251tostruct_in_srv(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
252 isc_region_t region;
253 dns_rdata_in_srv_t *srv = target;
254 dns_name_t name;
255
256 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
257 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
258 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
259 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
260
261 srv->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
262 srv->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
263 ISC_LINK_INIT(&srv->common, link);
264
265 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
266 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
267 srv->priority = uint16_fromregion(&region);
268 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
269 srv->weight = uint16_fromregion(&region);
270 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
271 srv->port = uint16_fromregion(&region);
272 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
273 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
274 dns_name_init(&srv->target, NULL);
275 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &srv->target));
276 srv->mctx = mctx;
277 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
278}
279
280static inline void
281freestruct_in_srv(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
282 dns_rdata_in_srv_t *srv = source;
283
284 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
285 REQUIRE(srv->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
286 REQUIRE(srv->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_srv);
287
288 if (srv->mctx == NULL)
289 return;
290
291 dns_name_free(&srv->target, srv->mctx);
292 srv->mctx = NULL;
293}

295static inline isc_result_t
296additionaldata_in_srv(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
297 char buf[sizeof("_65000._tcp")];
298 dns_fixedname_t fixed;
299 dns_name_t name;
300 dns_offsets_t offsets;
301 isc_region_t region;
302 uint16_t port;
303 isc_result_t result;
304
305 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
306 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
307
308 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
309 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
310 isc_region_consume(&region, 4);
311 port = uint16_fromregion(&region);
312 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
313 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
314
315 if (dns_name_equal(&name, dns_rootname))
316 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
317
318 result = (add)(arg, &name, dns_rdatatype_a);
319 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
320 return (result);
321
322 dns_fixedname_init(&fixed);
323 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "_%u._tcp", port);
324 result = dns_name_fromstring2(dns_fixedname_name(&fixed), buf, NULL,
325 0, NULL);
326 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
327 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
328
329 result = dns_name_concatenate(dns_fixedname_name(&fixed), &name,
330 dns_fixedname_name(&fixed), NULL);
331 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
332 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
333
334 return ((add)(arg, dns_fixedname_name(&fixed), dns_rdatatype_tlsa));
335}

337static inline isc_result_t
338digest_in_srv(ARGS_DIGEST) {
339 isc_region_t r1, r2;
340 dns_name_t name;
341
342 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
343 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
344
345 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r1);
346 r2 = r1;
347 isc_region_consume(&r2, 6);
348 r1.length = 6;
349 RETERR((digest)(arg, &r1));
350 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
351 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r2);
352 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
353}

355static inline bool
356checkowner_in_srv(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
357
358 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
359 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
360
361 UNUSED(name);
362 UNUSED(type);
363 UNUSED(rdclass);
364 UNUSED(wildcard);
365
366 return (true);
367}
368
369static inline bool
370checknames_in_srv(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
371 isc_region_t region;
372 dns_name_t name;
373
374 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_srv);
375 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
376
377 UNUSED(owner);
378
379 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
380 isc_region_consume(&region, 6);
381 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
382 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
383 if (!dns_name_ishostname(&name, false)) {
384 if (bad != NULL)
385 dns_name_clone(&name, bad);
386 return (false);
387 }
388 return (true);
389}
390
391static inline int
392casecompare_in_srv(ARGS_COMPARE) {
393 return (compare_in_srv(rdata1, rdata2));
394}
